.DT
add_sign
Disk World creator help
add_sign

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_sign -  This method adds a sign into the room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs object add_sign(string sign_long,
mixed sign_read_mess,
string sign_short,
mixed sign_name,
string sign_language)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^sign_long%^RESET%^ - the long description of the sign
%^BOLD%^sign_read_mess%^RESET%^ - the readable message on the sign
%^BOLD%^sign_short%^RESET%^ - the short description of the sign
%^BOLD%^sign_name%^RESET%^ - the name of the sign
%^BOLD%^sign_language%^RESET%^ - the language the sign is written in
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the object for the sign
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic_room_new.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a sign into the room.  Any of these elements can
be set to 0, except the long description.
.EP

